{"tid":1881683,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"唔好聽機人之魂亂up,日本人行去中國化運動有無放棄打麻雀？？有無唔再食飯用筷子？？","createTime":"2020-02-15T17:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T09:28:10.000Z","uid":22675,"like":24,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"74e70d3e5bf817fa2f7bf575caf1b2ef1e6f1b0b","tid":1881683,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T17:10:31.000Z","msg":"放棄中國文化唔等同於連自己文化都要捨棄，相反就係為咗保護自己獨有文化避免比中華文化入侵，先要脫離中華文化！！我見連登不斷用共產中文就係中華文化入侵香港文化嘅証據，再唔同中華文化一刀兩斷香港文化裡面嘅獨有詞語好快就會失傳，狗仔，手電，低調處理呢啲詞語請問大家有幾多年無用過？？完全畀狗狗，手x（機字太不雅用x代替），冷處理取代曬，跟住又話係唔同意思所以無問題，總之用大量借口合理化自己用共產中文！！"},{"pid":"718efad2abac6ab17c89882ae1619a227c989fbf","tid":1881683,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T17:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78a205d07b78863e9b4f8b95143810c6c1db7f23","tid":1881683,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"718efad2abac6ab17c89882ae1619a227c989fbf","tid":1881683,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T17:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T17:21:41.000Z","msg":"手電？<br />\n定手提"},{"pid":"2734e094c9fb280dd36e2d1f3c4af48e924f9897","tid":1881683,"uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"78a205d07b78863e9b4f8b95143810c6c1db7f23","tid":1881683,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"718efad2abac6ab17c89882ae1619a227c989fbf","tid":1881683,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T17:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T17:21:41.000Z","msg":"手電？<br />\n定手提"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T17:31:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/28/152441_556428a0a734ebfab3b1f2f76d9143c3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=